        "En": "Encyclopedia Judaica\n\nhttp://www.mestobechyne.cz/en/english/the-town-of-bechyne/jewsh-cemetery.html\n\nhttp://www.iajgsjewishcemeteryproject.org/czech-republic/bechyne.html", 
        "He": "\u05de\u05e7\u05d5\u05e8\u05d5\u05ea, \u05de\u05e8\u05d9\u05dd \u05d4\u05d9\u05d9\u05e0\u05dc"
