        "En": "Encyclopedia Judaica\n\nList, Miriam Hajnal\n\nhttp://www.iajgsjewishcemeteryproject.org/czech-republic/bucovice.html\n\nhttp://www.south-moravia.info/bucovice/13_5142_bucovice-jewish-cemetery/\n\nThe Encyclopedia of Jewish Life Before and During the Holocaust: A-J, Spector, Shmuel, Wigoder, Geoffrey, eds.\n", 
        "He": "\u05de\u05e7\u05d5\u05e8\u05d5\u05ea, \u05de\u05e8\u05d9\u05dd \u05d4\u05d9\u05d9\u05e0\u05dc"
